videos.headline: Stoner gets behind Baylor's defense for an Oklahoma State 75-yard TD
videos.description: Spencer Sanders buys time and launches it deep to an open Dillon Stoner who caps off the 75-yard catch with a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Stoner gets behind Baylor's defense for an Oklahoma State 75-yard TD) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stoner shrugs off a defender for his third TD for Oklahoma State
videos.description: Spencer Sanders lets it fly deep to Dillon Stoner, who breaks free of his defender to score his third touchdown of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Stoner shrugs off a defender for his third TD for Oklahoma State) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Richardson powers his way in for TD
videos.description: Dominic Richardson scores his first collegiate touchdown with a little muscle as he runs in from 17 yards out.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Oklahoma State's Richardson powers his way in for TD) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor's Brown fights for the end zone INT
videos.description: Zeke Brown battles for the interception on an intended touchdown pass from Spencer Sanders.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baylor's Brown fights for the end zone INT) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: OK State's Richardson gets banged up but scores another TD
videos.description: Dominic Richardson takes a few hits but will not be denied the short two-yard touchdown for Oklahoma State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (OK State's Richardson gets banged up but scores another TD) 2020/12/12 ESHEET
